sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / AI Tool
    participant MCP as MCP Server<br/>(server/mcp_server.py)
    participant Tools as tools/
    participant Cls as classifier.py
    participant Ctx as context_builder.py
    participant Rtr as router.py
    participant Mem as memory/ + retrieval/
    participant Model as Model API<br/>(Claude / Gemini / Grok)
    participant Store as .cognirepo/

    User->>MCP: JSON-RPC tool call
    MCP->>Tools: route to tool function
    Tools->>Mem: retrieve / store
    Mem->>Store: read/write FAISS + graph + episodic

    Note over User,MCP: CLI ask path
    User->>Cls: cognirepo ask "..."
    Cls-->>User: tier = QUICK|FAST|BALANCED|DEEP
    Cls->>Ctx: hydrate ContextBundle
    Ctx->>Mem: semantic + graph + AST + episodic + session
    Ctx->>Rtr: ContextBundle + tier
    Rtr->>Model: prompt + context
    Model-->>Rtr: response
    Rtr->>Store: session.append_exchange()
    Rtr-->>User: answer
